{"v":"1.0","id":"georacle-h13-placement-content-v1","date":"2026-07-05","house":13,"role":["querent-witness","問卜者見證轉化"],"method":{"directPriority":"SRC-003 page-verified direct special-house passages","contextualFallback":"SRC-013 page-verified elemental-house passages only when direct special-house evidence is absent","guardrails":["contextual elemental-house evidence is not relabeled as direct H13-H16 evidence","structural non-appearance statements are not converted into malefic judgments","same-family SRC-010 is not counted as an independent vote","H13/H14 are not past/future","H15 is not four-element synthesis","H16 is not presumed malefic"]},"records":[{"id":"plc-puer-h13","f":"puer","h":13,"home":1,"el":"火","core":"問卜者一側先經壓力與悲傷後尋求脫困；同時帶有旅行、消息、遠人與情愛連接的動勢。","fav":["脫離艱難","出現部分好轉","情感連接","消息或遠人帶動變化"],"unfav":["焦慮","旅途受驚","忙亂","情感衝動"],"status":"page-verified-direct","refs":[{"sourceId":"SRC-003","pages":[67],"supportType":"direct-special-house","pageVerified":true}],"notes":[],"conflicts":[]},{"id":"plc-laetitia-h13","f":"laetitia","h":13,"home":2,"el":"火","core":"問卜者一側的決心與推進意志增強；局勢偏向由內在信心帶動。","fav":["意志堅定","較能承擔","有利重整方向"],"unfav":["若把樂觀當成事實，可能低估阻力"],"status":"page-verified-direct","refs":[{"sourceId":"SRC-003","pages":[55],"supportType":"direct-special-house","pageVerified":true}],"notes":[],"conflicts":[]},{"id":"plc-caput-draconis-h13","f":"caput-draconis","h":13,"home":3,"el":"火","core":"問卜者一側偏向喜悅、安全、獲益、遠人歸來；但原文也提及與惡人交往，需防好機會被不良聯結污染。","fav":["喜悅","安全","獲益","遠人歸來"],"unfav":["與惡人交往","入口選錯"],"status":"page-verified-direct","refs":[{"sourceId":"SRC-003","pages":[105],"supportType":"direct-special-house","pageVerified":true}],"notes":[],"conflicts":[]},{"id":"plc-albus-h13","f":"albus","h":13,"home":4,"el":"火","core":"問卜者一側面臨敵方謀算與短暫停滯；耐心後凶勢可退，並可能由旅行與高位人士得到好處。","fav":["耐心後轉好","旅行得益","高位者助力","狀況修復"],"unfav":["敵方謀算","短暫停滯"],"status":"page-verified-direct","refs":[{"sourceId":"SRC-003","pages":[88],"supportType":"direct-special-house","pageVerified":true}],"notes":[],